|-
| PSBT Version Number
| <tt>PSBT_GLOBAL_VERSION = 0xFB</tt>
| [[../bip-0174.mediawiki|174]]
|-
| Proprietary Use Type
| <tt>PSBT_GLOBAL_PROPRIETARY = 0xFC</tt>
| [[../bip-0174.mediawiki|174]]
